"{\"uid\": \"eurasiareview.com-20062024-israel-should-be-banned-from-olympics-just-like-russia-oped\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A Journal of Analysis and News    ByRay Hanania  Russia and Belarus have both been banned from participating in the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics because of their involvement in the war on Ukraine.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 49, \"end\": 55, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999997843274518, \"rank\": 2.1507025523207634e-07, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 60, \"end\": 67, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"score\": 0.9999999999095053, \"rank\": 8.700190077908924e-11, \"text\": \"Belarus\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\"}, {\"begin\": 186, \"end\": 193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999541988770775, \"rank\": 4.5801373446052305e-05, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So why is Israel not being banned as well?\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 205, \"end\": 211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.658003320539982e-30, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Israel's military is engaged in one of the worst attacks on a civilian population since the Second World War, with more than 37,000 Palestinians killed in the Gaza Strip.\", \"from\": 239, \"to\": 409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.658003320539982e-30, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 371, \"end\": 383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.3313482190379317e-12, \"text\": \"Palestinians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}, {\"begin\": 398, \"end\": 408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4846176395524344e-21, \"text\": \"Gaza Strip\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And we only have Israel's word that many of those killed were members of Hamas, the militant group that launched a violent attack against Israel, killing about 1,200 people, on Oct. 7, 2023.\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 427, \"end\": 433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.658003320539982e-30, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1218198686866505e-25, \"text\": \"Hamas\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\"}, {\"begin\": 548, \"end\": 554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.658003320539982e-30, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the first two years following Russia's invasion of Ukraine in February 2022, more than 30,000 Ukrainians were killed or wounded.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 635, \"end\": 641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999997843274518, \"rank\": 2.1507025523207634e-07, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 656, \"end\": 663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999541988770775, \"rank\": 4.5801373446052305e-05, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 699, \"end\": 709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainians\", \"score\": 0.9378104193725252, \"rank\": 0.06631359530866482, \"text\": \"Ukrainians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are actually more specific details on how Ukrainians are being killed by Russia than there are on Israel's reckless military bombardment of nearly every city in the Gaza Strip.\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 917, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 783, \"end\": 793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainians\", \"score\": 0.9378104193725252, \"rank\": 0.06631359530866482, \"text\": \"Ukrainians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainians\"}, {\"begin\": 814, \"end\": 820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999997843274518, \"rank\": 2.1507025523207634e-07, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 839, \"end\": 845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.658003320539982e-30, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 906, \"end\": 916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4846176395524344e-21, \"text\": \"Gaza Strip\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The details of the violence against Ukraine is so specific that humanitarian and aid organizations have pinned down the casualty rate to 42 civilians every day.\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 1078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 954, \"end\": 961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999541988770775, \"rank\": 4.5801373446052305e-05, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than 87 percent of the Ukrainians killed, or 9,241 people, were casualties of explosive weapons.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1108, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainians\", \"score\": 0.9378104193725252, \"rank\": 0.06631359530866482, \"text\": \"Ukrainians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than 5.9 million people have been forced to flee Ukraine to other countries and about 4 million are displaced within Ukraine.\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1312, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1236, \"end\": 1243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999541988770775, \"rank\": 4.5801373446052305e-05, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 1304, \"end\": 1311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999541988770775, \"rank\": 4.5801373446052305e-05, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Gaza, nearly 85 percent of the population of 2.3 million have been forced from their homes and are constantly seeking shelter.\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1317, \"end\": 1321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 0.9999999634023886, \"rank\": 3.659742547008775e-08, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Israel not only fires missiles into the imprisoned land mass, but it has also sent tanks, troops and snipers into the area, killing targets as they move from Beit Lahia in the north to Rafah in the south.\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1444, \"end\": 1450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.658003320539982e-30, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 1602, \"end\": 1612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beit_Lahia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.435190193359949e-57, \"text\": \"Beit Lahia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beit_Lahia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beit_Lahia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The host of this year's Olympics, France, is divided on the Israeli invasion and the government has taken action to oppose a rise in antisemitism.\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1796, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1684, \"end\": 1690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9933208266002967, \"rank\": 0.005529430639950917, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 1710, \"end\": 1717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9592101731595712, \"rank\": 0.0243556301368094, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French President Emmanuel Macron has also offered consoling words to Muslims.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1797, \"end\": 1813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1814, \"end\": 1829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1866, \"end\": 1873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.999880378882335, \"rank\": 0.00010021209875796525, \"text\": \"Muslims\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why has the International Olympic Committee not taken action to curtail or prohibit Israel's participation in the Olympics?\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1888, \"end\": 1919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1960, \"end\": 1966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.658003320539982e-30, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the international rule of law and the West's supposed opposition to the killing of civilians had any meaning, Israel would be banned.\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2113, \"end\": 2119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.658003320539982e-30, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The problem is that, when it comes to the Middle East, the West has always cared less about the suffering of Arabs and Muslims than the suffering of non-Arabs and non-Muslims.\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2247, \"end\": 2252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arab_citizens_of_Israel\", \"score\": 0.9999713837502877, \"rank\": 2.8544849651983274e-05, \"text\": \"Arabs\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arab_citizens_of_Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arab_citizens_of_Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 2257, \"end\": 2264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.999880378882335, \"rank\": 0.00010021209875796525, \"text\": \"Muslims\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is that racist and Islamophobic attitude, which is driven by ugly historical stereotypes that date back to the Crusades of almost 1,000 years ago, that allows the West to be concerned for Ukraine and angry with Russia, while being unconcerned about Arabs in Gaza and throughout the Middle East and accepting of Israel.\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2336, \"end\": 2348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamophobia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8994414866556184e-31, \"text\": \"Islamophobic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamophobia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamophobia\"}, {\"begin\": 2505, \"end\": 2512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999541988770775, \"rank\": 4.5801373446052305e-05, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 2528, \"end\": 2534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999997843274518, \"rank\": 2.1507025523207634e-07, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 2566, \"end\": 2571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arab_citizens_of_Israel\", \"score\": 0.9999713837502877, \"rank\": 2.8544849651983274e-05, \"text\": \"Arabs\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arab_citizens_of_Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arab_citizens_of_Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 2575, \"end\": 2579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 0.9999999634023886, \"rank\": 3.659742547008775e-08, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}, {\"begin\": 2628, \"end\": 2634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.658003320539982e-30, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Israel largely controls the media narrative of the war, falsely asserting that the violence began on Oct. 7.\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2637, \"end\": 2643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.658003320539982e-30, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Western news media has generally championed that narrative, carrying water for Israel.\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2836, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2746, \"end\": 2762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Western_News\", \"score\": 0.9999999902461241, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Western news\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Western_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Western_News\"}, {\"begin\": 2829, \"end\": 2835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.658003320539982e-30, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Israel has engaged in a war not only against Hamas, but also against independent, mainly Arab journalists, killing more than 100 of those who have been reporting on the war from Gaza and who have not been embedded with Israel's military, which censors and controls content.\", \"from\": 2838, \"to\": 3122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2849, \"end\": 2855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.658003320539982e-30, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 2894, \"end\": 2899, \"title