e/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Israeli military censorship in both Gaza and the West Bank since the start of the occupation in 1967 means it is tough to know the exact number of Palestinians who have been killed, as well as the extent of the land theft that continues to take place in order to build and expand Jewish-only settlements.\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3452, \"end\": 3468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.585586313608383e-68, \"text\": \"Israeli military\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\"}, {\"begin\": 3488, \"end\": 3492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 0.9999999634023886, \"rank\": 3.659742547008775e-08, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}, {\"begin\": 3501, \"end\": 3510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Bank\", \"score\": 0.9999163539866155, \"rank\": 8.365301057537256e-05, \"text\": \"West Bank\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Bank\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Bank\"}, {\"begin\": 3599, \"end\": 3611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.3313482190379317e-12, \"text\": \"Palestinians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Estimates of the number of Palestinians killed in 2023 before Oct. 7 range from 175 to 230, while in 2022 it was between 250 and 400.\", \"from\": 3758, \"to\": 3891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3785, \"end\": 3797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.3313482190379317e-12, \"text\": \"Palestinians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"B'Tselem, the Israeli human rights organization, tries to maintain its own list but, several years ago, Israel's government cracked down on such humanitarian and human rights groups.\", \"from\": 3892, \"to\": 4074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3906, \"end\": 3913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9592101731595712, \"rank\": 0.0243556301368094, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 3996, \"end\": 4002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.658003320539982e-30, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021, B'Tselem carried out exhaustive research and detailed its findings in a document that concluded that Israel was carrying out apartheid policies that discriminated against non-Jews.\", \"from\": 4076, \"to\": 4265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4085, \"end\": 4093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/B'Tselem\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"B'Tselem\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/B'Tselem\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/B'Tselem\"}, {\"begin\": 4186, \"end\": 4192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.658003320539982e-30, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Months later, Israel's government declared six prominent Palestinian human rights groups to be \\\"terrorist organizations,\\\" curbing their ability to document Israel's human rights abuses and its military and police violence against non-Jews.\", \"from\": 4267, \"to\": 4506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4281, \"end\": 4287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.658003320539982e-30, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 4324, \"end\": 4335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.9999999999636202, \"rank\": 1.9466978157327958e-11, \"text\": \"Palestinian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}, {\"begin\": 4423, \"end\": 4429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.658003320539982e-30, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, following the Hamas attack, with Palestinian organizations silenced by Israel's restrictive policies and threats, B'Tselem documented how Israel's invasion of Gaza was emphasizing violence against civilians.\", \"from\": 4508, \"to\": 4724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4531, \"end\": 4536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1218198686866505e-25, \"text\": \"Hamas\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\"}, {\"begin\": 4550, \"end\": 4561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.9999999999636202, \"rank\": 1.9466978157327958e-11, \"text\": \"Palestinian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\",